OL,4,C'relatively modest' compensation
OL,6,FDuring the summer, the Government set
OL,7,Fout that infected and affected victims
OL,8,Fwill receive a series of financial
OL,9,Fawards depending on their
OL,10,Fcircumstances, including for "injury
OL,11,Fimpact", "social impact", "autonomy",
OL,12,F"care" and "financial loss".
OL,14,FBut the Government will pay an
OL,15,Fadditional #10,000 sum to people who
OL,16,Fwere part of unethical research
OL,17,Fprojects on top of these awards or
OL,18,F#15,000 to victims who attended Lord
OL,19,FMayor Treloar College in Alton,
OL,20,FHampshire.
