OL,6,FOf the pupils that attended Lord Mayor
OL,7,FTreloar College in the 1970s and
OL,8,F1980s, "very few escaped being
OL,9,Finfected."and of 122 pupils with
OL,10,Fhaemophilia that attended the school
OL,11,Fbetween 1970 and 1987, only around 30
OL,12,Fare still alive.
OL,14,FMr Efford, MP for Eltham and
OL,15,FChislehurst, told the Commons: "My
OL,16,Fconstituent is a former Treloar's
OL,17,Fpupil and he is upset about the
OL,18,F#15,000 payment and doesn't think it's
OL,19,Fanywhere near enough.
