OL,6,F"I think what this shows is those
OL,7,Fpeople who've been campaigning for 40
OL,8,Fyears want to be more involved in the
OL,9,Fdecisions that are being made about
OL,10,Fthem.
OL,12,F"I certainly want to hear how they are
OL,13,Fgoing to be engaged, so that they can
OL,14,Fmake their voices heard about the
OL,15,Fissues whilst welcoming generally what
OL,16,Fhas been proposed, they want to be
OL,17,Fable to influence things as they go
OL,18,Fforwards."
