OL,6,FCabinet Office minister Nick Thomas-
OL,7,FSymonds replied: "I think that the
OL,8,Fconsultation exercise which took place
OL,9,Fduring the period of the general
OL,10,Felection campaign was hugely important.
OL,12,F"I think it was important the
OL,13,FGovernment listened and made the
OL,14,Fsubstantial changes to the scheme that
OL,15,Fwe have done.
OL,17,F"It is hugely important too that the
OL,18,Fvoice of victims continues to be heard
OL,19,Fas the infected blood compensation
OL,20,Fscheme continues its work."
