OL,6,FMr Thomas-Symonds said the #15,000
OL,7,Ffigure was a recommendation from Sir
OL,8,FRobert Francis, who helped set up the
OL,9,FInfected Blood Compensation Authority
OL,10,F(IBCA).
OL,12,F"It is a marker of the appalling and
OL,13,Funethical medical research," the
OL,14,Fminister said.
