OL,6,FShadow paymaster general John Glen had
OL,7,Fearlier said: "I would ask the
OL,8,FPaymaster General to clarify the
OL,9,Fadditional autonomy awards for
OL,10,Funethical medical research and
OL,11,Fespecially for the nearly 100
OL,12,Fhaemophiliac children from Treloar's
OL,13,Fwho the Government has now stated will
OL,14,Fbe paid a higher #15,000 award.
OL,16,F"There have been reported comments
OL,17,Ffrom some in the Treloar's community
OL,18,Fwho appear unhappy at these relatively
OL,19,Fmodest supplementary amounts."
