OL,4,C'relatively modest' compensation
OL,6,FMr Thomas-Symonds told MPs: "I should
OL,7,Fsay to the House that, look, there is
OL,8,Fno amount of money that is ever going
OL,9,Fto make up for the horrors that we've
OL,10,Fseen as part of this scheme."
OL,12,FHe added: "That (#15,000) will form
OL,13,Fbut a small part of the overall
OL,14,Famounts that I would expect to be paid
OL,15,Fout under this scheme."
OL,17,FMr Glen also said: "It continues to
OL,18,Ftrouble me that those who determined
OL,19,Fthis research should take place in the
OL,20,Ffirst place appear unaccountable for
OL,21,Fthose decisions."
