OL,6,FThe minister replied: "Individual
OL,7,Fprosecutorial decisions are quite
OL,8,Frightly independent decisions for the
OL,9,Fprosecuting authorities.
OL,11,F"But I can confirm that on 9 August, I
OL,12,Fwrote to the National Police Chiefs'
OL,13,FCouncil... to make clear that the
OL,14,FCabinet Office and indeed the
OL,15,FGovernment will co-operate fully and
OL,16,Fmake any evidence that is within our
OL,17,Fcontrol and possession available as
OL,18,Fappropriate so decisions can be made
OL,19,Fabout people being held to account."
